--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: LocalTable_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: aac8ceb655d3e9940afa077145e80ad1, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 10001
    m_Localized: It appears even the solace of death is denied to me, as the scent
      of cold, damp earth begins to permeate my senses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10002
    m_Localized: Not a shred of flesh remains. leaving only these crumbling shards
      of bone to sustain my existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10003
    m_Localized: How dare, contemptible beast desecrate the hallowed grounds where
      my kin find their eternal rest.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10004
    m_Localized: I shall not permit your foul fangs to desecrate the sanctity of
      my kin's remains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20001
    m_Localized: Grrr... Death's prey has returned. Your broken screams...they were
      nectar to my ears.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20002
    m_Localized: No more screams. Only the sound of your end.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20003
    m_Localized: Grrr... A rattling skull! My axe buries you in the abyss. Never
      to rise again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20004
    m_Localized: Tell Death. He lost grip. Now, I rise to crush your wretched world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20005
    m_Localized: The beginning. Your blood to soak this barren earth.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20006
    m_Localized: "Arrogant worm! I\u2019ll grind your spite to dust. No rest for
      you. Ever!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20007
    m_Localized: Grrr... With your rusted crown, I turn this dirt into a slaughterhouse!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20008
    m_Localized: Abominable malice stains the silence of my frost. A king whose soul
      was torn by Death itself... why do you still haunt the living with your cold
      breath?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20009
    m_Localized: Their frozen tears, still wet. No rest until I pierce your heart.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20010
    m_Localized: Foolish creature. You dare defy the sanctity of death for a mere
      grudge? This time, I shall freeze your very spite until it shatters into a
      thousand shards.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20011
    m_Localized: Speak not of providence. Here, only my vengeance and your end remain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20012
    m_Localized: "Crowned phantom! I shall begin by freezing those arrogant eyes
      of yours. This is my domain\u2014where neither the living nor the dead are
      permitted to linger!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20013
    m_Localized: (Black mist splits. and there, Death emerges, trailing a colossal
      scythe behind.)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20014
    m_Localized: At last, thou hast reached the end... O King of a fallen realm.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20015
    m_Localized: O King who denied eternal rest... Hast thou defied the providence
      for a mere grudge?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20016
    m_Localized: Rest? Did you grant them rest while your scythe reaped their souls?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20017
    m_Localized: To force your hollow eyes to witness my hell, I rose from the dead.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20018
    m_Localized: A hollow obsession. The fall of a kingdom and the fading of its
      people... it is the same providence as water flowing to the depths. You, too,
      were but a single ripple in that current.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20019
    m_Localized: I returned to shatter that providence. The day my crown broke and
      my heart failed, I cast aside my humanity.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20020
    m_Localized: Now, only your head to fall, and your world to crumble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20021
    m_Localized: "Pitiable soul. I shall teach thee the brevity of thy wrath. When
      the sands run dry, thy grand vengeance\u2014and thy name\u2014shall be swallowed
      by the ever-silent void."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20022
    m_Localized: Grant me your screams, Death. This is no longer your hunting ground.
      It is your grave.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20023
    m_Localized: The moment the Death falls, the darkness shatters into a thousand
      shards.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20024
    m_Localized: As the burning thirst for vengeance fades, the phantom world sustained
      by the King's obsession dissolves... returning at last to the stillness of
      its original grave.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20025
    m_Localized: "From within the King\u2019s breast, the shards of the Princess\u2019s
      soul spill forth, weaving a form of pure radiance. Amidst the glow, she appears\u2014folding
      her father's skeletal frame into a tender embrace."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20026
    m_Localized: Enough, my King. Yield your heavy steel, and find your solace in
      peace
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20027
    m_Localized: "At the touch of the Princess\u2019s voice, the bitter malice and
      obsession that held the King captive are washed away."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20028
    m_Localized: No longer consumed by blind vengeance, he returns to himself. not
      as a wraith of war, but as the King of Serilda, preparing for his peaceful
      rest.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20029
    m_Localized: Yes... It was a very long dream...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20030
    m_Localized: At last, I can rest.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20031
    m_Localized: The obsession has lifted, and the dawn has broken at last. May you
      find a place where your hands need never touch a blade again
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20032
    m_Localized: At last... even the flame of this life flickers out, leaving its
      great purpose to the ashes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20033
    m_Localized: Even the searing malice of your vengeance scatters now as frozen
      ash. this moment, as it returns, pierces my heart with a chilling sorrow.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30001
    m_Localized: The forge still burns. To reach the end of my vengeance, I must
      be armed in cruelty.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30002
    m_Localized: 'Sharpen the blade keenly. [ATK+1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30003
    m_Localized: A finer edge. One strike, one silence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30004
    m_Localized: 'enhance the rusted armor. [DEF+1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30005
    m_Localized: Shed this rusted plate. I must refit it to my very bones. Hard enough
      to deny a counterattack.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30006
    m_Localized: You have come, my Lord... Even in this freezing darkness, we waited
      only for the sound of your footsteps.\n The failure was ours, My Lord. Do not
      let guilt stay your hand. Please keep moving forward.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30007
    m_Localized: 'Heal the wounds with the breath of the people. [Heal 50]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30008
    m_Localized: Cease your sorrow. Let our fading lives mend your broken spirit.
      Stand tall once more, and lead us forward.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30009
    m_Localized: 'Consecrate the life force of the people to the heart. [REC+1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30010
    m_Localized: My Lord... take our final breath of life. Though our souls scatter
      to the wind, let us become your heart and fill the vessel. Do not let your
      spirit break.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30011
    m_Localized: Dusty treaties remain. Though the flesh is gone, the tactical gambits
      that shook the battlefield must be reawakened.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30012
    m_Localized: 'Tactics: Swift Move. [SP+1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30013
    m_Localized: "A swift strike. A masterpiece of war\u2014leaving no room for reaction."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30014
    m_Localized: 'Tactics: Rapid Volley. [APG+1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30015
    m_Localized: "The flow of the fray. One strike to feed the next\u2014a relentless
      chain of slaughter."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30016
    m_Localized: "A long, weary road you\u2019ve walked... Hehehe... You look so
      tired, my poor, broken King. \\n I see it clinging to your straight back...
      a bitter loneliness and a thirst for vengeance. Won't you stay a while and
      ask this old crone for the way?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30017
    m_Localized: 'Seek the old woman''s advice. [ATK+2, DEF-1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30018
    m_Localized: "My poor, pitied King... Listen to this old crone's whispers. Your
      guard may grow frail and your armor thin, but in exchange, I shall teach you
      a ruinous gambit\u2014one that will drive your blade deep into the very heart
      of your foe."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30019
    m_Localized: 'Embrace the old woman.[HP-50%, APG+1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30020
    m_Localized: "Hehehe... Yes, my pitied King. Sink deeper into these withered
      arms. I shall take half the life that sustains you, but in return, I will make
      those dry bones strike with a speed you\u2019ve never known."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30021
    m_Localized: Even under a shattered sky, you seek a path. Your light has fallen,
      yet a single chance lingers in the warped orbit. Shall I unveil it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30022
    m_Localized: 'Overlap the threads of fate. [ADD +30%]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30023
    m_Localized: The stars have crossed. Fate flows through your steel, and soon,
      a moment of unpredictable power shall unfurl. Will you place your faith in
      the luck of the high heavens?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30024
    m_Localized: 'Glimpse the twisted timeline. [ADD+100%]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30025
    m_Localized: A fractured future... Your steps grow heavy, but your blade now
      bears a second destiny. Every strike carries a shard of cruel fate. The price
      is yours to bear.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30026
    m_Localized: "To step into this ruin... my broken Lord, if my prayer can bring
      even a moment\u2019s rest to your shattered frame, I shall gladly bless the
      path you tread"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30027
    m_Localized: 'Receive the Martyr''s prayer. [REC-1, MaxHP+20]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30028
    m_Localized: May this prayer be a flicker of light upon your path. Though the
      power to heal your wounds may wane, the weight of your soul that you can now
      bear will be deeper and broader than ever before.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30029
    m_Localized: 'Take the remaining divine power.[REC+1, MaxHP-10]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30030
    m_Localized: Nothing but hollow screams here. Your maximum life will wither,
      yet the holy grace mending your wounds shall blaze with unrivaled intensity.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30031
    m_Localized: 'Spiteful phantom, wandering the dark... I grant the strength you
      crave. Yet remember: what the hand takes, the soul must repay.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30032
    m_Localized: 'Accept the angel''s merciful touch. [HP 50% under, REC+2]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30033
    m_Localized: Your yearning shall be the light. when your HP drops below half,
      the Sacred Touch will reach deeper into your wounds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30034
    m_Localized: 'Don the angel''s holy protection. [HP 50% over, DEP+1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30035
    m_Localized: Full of energy is your steadfast shield. While your form is whole,
      a Heavenly Aegis shall bolster you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30036
    m_Localized: "Keke... Your searing heart led me here. Your soul\u2019s ruin is
      nothing to me. You want the power for revenge? Then pay the price. A life for
      a life, a soul for a soul."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30037
    m_Localized: 'Contract with the demon. [HP 30% under, ATK+2]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30038
    m_Localized: Very well. When you dance with death, your blade shall unleash a
      cataclysm. Enjoy your ruinous power. The deal is done.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30039
    m_Localized: 'Offer vitality to the demon. [HP40% under, APG+1]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30040
    m_Localized: I take your life as my tribute. In exchange, I shall grant you a
      fearsome speed. That fleeting moment will be your final, dying flame.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30041
    m_Localized: The wind has shifted... To think a pulsing heart still beats in
      this barren land. The children of the forest are curious about your wounded
      soul. Will you accept their playful blessing?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30042
    m_Localized: 'Absorb the spirit''s vital flow. [Drain HP (Dmg20%)]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30043
    m_Localized: Heed the river of life. Breathe in the grace that nature yields.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30044
    m_Localized: 'Be promised the forest''s last protection. [Resurrection, HP +50]'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 30045
    m_Localized: The forest promises protection. As your light fades, the spirits
      will ignite their souls to bring you back. A miracle granted but once.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40001
    m_Localized: My Lord... even death could not hold your grievance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40002
    m_Localized: Can you feel it, My Lord? The unseen hand that guides you... an
      escapable pull within this wretched wheel.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40003
    m_Localized: My Lord... let this be your final journey. To the rest you so rightly
      earned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40004
    m_Localized: Remember, my Lord. Though your flesh is gone, the royal power carved
      into your soul still breathes within this grid.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40005
    m_Localized: Seize a shard of thought and slide it aside. That fleeting shift
      shall decide your destiny.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40006
    m_Localized: Be wary. A false judgment will only gnaw at his remaining breath.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40007
    m_Localized: With every shard you shift, shattered soul will slowly fade.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40008
    m_Localized: Align three shards of a single hue. That fleeting union shall ignite
      a flare to consume them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40009
    m_Localized: Choose wisely. Shards may grant great power, or they may do nothing
      at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40010
    m_Localized: The crimson shards are your piercing steel. Align them to strike
      a mortal blow.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40011
    m_Localized: Blue shards are your shield. Align them to block their malice.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40012
    m_Localized: Pink shards are your broken heart. Align them to mend your fading
      life.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40013
    m_Localized: Green shards are your royal arts. Align them to prepare a surging
      tide.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
